xit-strategy-as-egypt-fights-to-keep-talks-alive/00000191-79ac-dacb-afb3-f9bf55ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列无人机袭击约旦河西岸图勒凯尔姆，造成三名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-drone-strike-in-west-banks-tulkarm-ministry-says/00000191-79b4-daab-a3f3-f9b61b0e0000</link><description>以色列军方表示，这架无人机的目标是一群对以色列国防军和辛贝特部队构成危险的武装人员，这些武装人员从周四开始在该市进行行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-drone-strike-in-west-banks-tulkarm-ministry-says/00000191-79b4-daab-a3f3-f9b61b0e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军检察官：斯德泰曼士兵殴打、电击、鸡奸加沙被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecutor-sde-teiman-soldiers-beat-electrified-sodomized-gaza-detainee/00000191-796d-de08-a3f9-796f17e00000</link><description>上个月被捕的五名以色列国防军士兵被指控严重虐待一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者。军事检察官要求他们再软禁两周</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecutor-sde-teiman-soldiers-beat-electrified-sodomized-gaza-detainee/00000191-796d-de08-a3f9-796f17e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队逮捕了四名西岸嫌疑人，罪名是“针对巴勒斯坦人的恐怖行为”，其中包括在吉特发生致命暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-arrest-four-west-bank-suspects-for-terrorist-acts-against-palestinians/00000191-7936-d2f3-afdf-7dffd68d0000</link><description>这是与巴勒斯坦西岸吉特村定居者骚乱有关的首次逮捕，一名巴勒斯坦人被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-arrest-four-west-bank-suspects-for-terrorist-acts-against-palestinians/00000191-7936-d2f3-afdf-7dffd68d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果与哈马斯和真主党的消耗战继续下去，以色列将在一年内崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-will-collapse-within-a-year-if-the-war-against-hamas-and-hezbollah-continues/00000191-795e-d8d0-a7bb-f9ff81000000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:44:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-will-collapse-within-a-year-if-the-war-against-hamas-and-hezbollah-continues/00000191-795e-d8d0-a7bb-f9ff81000000</guid></item><item><title>让煽动反对加沙人的立法者摆脱困境将使以色列在海牙付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/letting-lawmakers-who-incite-against-gazans-off-the-hook-will-cost-israel-in-the-hague/00000191-748f-dc26-a9d7-f49ffe910000</link><description>部长们和议会议员没有约束加沙“热血沸腾”的士兵，而是鼓励他们攻击巴勒斯坦平民。总检察长必须无视国家检察官不要调查他们的建议，但他的决定已经玷污了以色列的执法系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/letting-lawmakers-who-incite-against-gazans-off-the-hook-will-cost-israel-in-the-hague/00000191-748f-dc26-a9d7-f49ffe910000</guid></item><item><title>“粉碎哈马斯”与“带他们回家”：以色列人质如何成为丑陋政治游戏中的棋子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</link><description>呼吁释放加沙人质的活动人士感到，这是他们核心民族身份的紧迫性，而以色列右翼则认为，任何协议都将有助于激励哈马斯。如果内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们考虑到这些困境就好了</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:32:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么现在与真主党的停火协议对以色列不利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</link><description>正如国际调解人所希望的那样，将加沙和黎巴嫩的停战协议联系起来，将使主张消除主义的真主党取得宣传胜利，并对以色列的威慑和防御造成危险的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</guid></item><item><title>一个新的危险阶段：以色列与哈马斯未能达成协议将加剧中东地区更广泛冲突的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</link><description>美国最近对确保停火的乐观态度可能被夸大了。虽然布林肯的出席确保真主党或伊朗不会在民主党全国代表大会期间对以色列进行报复，但情报显示黎巴嫩武装分子决心很快发动报复袭击。在华盛顿，希望奇迹至少还能再持续一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称从加沙打捞上来的六名人质尸体中发现枪伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军对约旦河西岸图尔卡姆的袭击造成三人死亡 ■ 火箭袭击以色列北部时，以色列国防军袭击了真主党目标 ■ 拜登在与内塔尼亚胡通话时强调达成加沙协议的“紧迫性” ■ 内塔尼亚胡誓言以色列空军已做好应对任何袭击的准备以色列北部的情况 ■ 以色列国防军称其在黎巴嫩击毙了伊斯兰革命卫队武装分子，并且战斗机在一夜之间击毙了真主党武装分子</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国以色列人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父母向《国土报》表示：我们对民主党全国委员会的积极接待感到震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们在民主党全国代表大会上发表讲话，高呼“带他们回家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</guid></item><item><title>在民主党全国委员会拒绝给巴勒斯坦裔美国发言人时间后，“不承诺”举行静坐抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</link><description>明尼苏达州州长基思·埃里森（Keith Ellison）直言不讳地批评以色列，他告诉代表们，“卡马拉·哈里斯在加沙问题上正在倾听我们的意见”，随后引发抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 01:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</guid></item><item><title>“现在是时候了”：美国-以色列人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父母在民主党全国委员会发表讲话，呼吁达成协议以结束痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们告诉民主党人，“在痛苦的竞争中，没有赢家”。人群中许多人高呼“带他们回家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:14:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普指责舒默是哈马斯成员，并指责民主党导致以色列输掉公关战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</link><description>前总统还对“犹太游说团体”失去影响力表示遗憾，如果这些评论来自对 AIPAC 等组织的民主党批评者，共和党人可能会谴责这些言论为反犹太主义。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列组织试图撤销巴勒斯坦记者的艾美奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</link><description>Bisan Atef Owda 制作的《这是加沙的 Bisan，我还活着》获得艾美奖提名。一家亲以色列的非营利组织写了一封公开信，称 Owda 与美国指定的恐怖组织 PFLP 有“记录在案的联系”，因此不应被提名</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在副总统哈里斯的陪同下与内塔尼亚胡通话，敦促加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</link><description>拜登政府高级官员表示，布林肯本周早些时候的言论造成了一种乐观和进步的错误感觉</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</guid></item><item><title>不要评判人质家属的痛苦，或者他们表达痛苦的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</link><description>当人质家属希望俘虏政治敌人的孩子而不是自己的孩子时，我们应该如何应对？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</guid></item><item><title>“政府希望以色列人过于担心自己的安全而忽视民主”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>